node.text: @jessieware please put an extra date on in Manchester!! 🤗

We are ridiculously excited to give the people what they want... Lennie Ware LIVE on stage! What started out as a chat in mums kitchen with just one person has turned into a tribe of food loving devotees and we cannot WAIT to bring @tablemannerspodcast up and down the country. Get ready for special guests, plenty of food,  and lots of FUN!! Tickets available right now, link in bio xx
